-- Hindustan Petroleum Said to Seek June-Loading Crude Via Tender
-- B y   R u p e r t   R o w l i n g
-- 2013-04-04T13:26:04Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-04-04/hindustan-petroleum-said-to-seek-june-loading-crude-via-tender.html
Hindustan Petroleum Corp.,  India ’s
third-largest state refiner, is seeking to buy crude for loading
from June 1 to June 30, according to two traders with knowledge
of the matter.  The company’s tender closes on April 8, and offers will
remain valid until the following day, according to the traders,
who asked not to be identified because the information is
confidential.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Rupert Rowling in London at 
 rrowling@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
